	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Get more colors to make logo -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">When making your logo move your logo move the cursor out of the painting area and hold L1 + L2 + R1 + R2 + Select. When the RGB option appears move the cursor to a color and press R1 + Up or Down</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Race on Backwards Tracks -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">After selecting Race Start hold L1 + R1 + Select + Start</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; View paint up close -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">While at the logo painting screen press L1 + L2 + R1 + R2 + Select</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Toggle Rear View Mirror -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">To turn off the rear view mirror, press the Start button to pause and then hold the Triangle button. While holding it, press the L1 button to make the mirror go away. If you want the mirror to return, keep holding Triangle button and press the R1 button instead.</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Max Speed -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8009DECE 03E7</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Infinite Money -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8019BFB0 FFFF<br>8019BFB2 00FF</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Always Place 1st -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8009DEDC 0001</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
