<table border="0" width="100%" id="table35" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="darkcell"  style="font-family: Trebuchet MS">
		<br>Thanks to <font color="#ACCDFB">ERIC SMITH</font> for providing the game front, inside, CD & Spine Card hires covers.
